==Honours==
{{col-begin}}
{{col-2}}
* 1976 – [[Grand Prix du Disque]] by [[L'Académie Charles Cros]], for ''Oxygène''&lt;ref name=&quot;Hughesp303&quot; /&gt;
* 1976 – &quot;Personality of The Year&quot; by ''[[People (American magazine)|People]]'' magazine (U.S.)&lt;ref name=&quot;Hughesp303&quot; /&gt;&lt;ref name=&quot;crying&quot;&gt;{{Citation | title = Crying all the way to the bank | url = https://www.theguardian.com/theguardian/2000/jan/10/features11.g21 | work = The Guardian| date = 10 January 2000 | accessdate = 20 June 2009}}&lt;/ref&gt;
* 1978 – [[Midem]] award&lt;ref&gt;{{Harvnb|Robertshaw|Jones|1978|p=58}}&lt;/ref&gt;
* 1979 – ''[[Guinness Book of Records]]'' entry for the biggest concert ever (La Concorde)&lt;ref name=&quot;Hughesp303&quot; /&gt;
* 1981 – Honorary member of the [[Beijing Conservatory of Music]].
* 1984 – [[Grand Prix du Disque]] by [[L'Académie Charles Cros]], for ''Zoolook''.&lt;ref name=&quot;oxygeneconcert&quot; /&gt;
* 1985 – Instrumental album of the year, at the [[Victoires de la Musique]] in France, for ''Zoolook''&lt;ref name=&quot;oxygeneconcert&quot;&gt;{{Citation | title = Oxygène Live in Concert 2008 | publisher = Hill Shorter Ltd (printer) | pages = 10–11 | year = 2008}}&lt;/ref&gt;
