* 1986 – Musical spectacle of the year, at the [[Victoires de la Musique]], for the Rendez-Vous Houston concert&lt;ref name=&quot;oxygeneconcert&quot; /&gt;
* 1987 – New ''[[Guinness Book of Records]]'' entry for the biggest concert ever ([[Rendez-Vous Houston]])&lt;ref name=&quot;Porticop86&quot; /&gt;
* 1987 – &quot;European musician Person of the Year&quot; by ''People'' magazine&lt;ref name=&quot;oxygeneconcert&quot; /&gt;
* 1990 – New ''[[Guinness Book of Records]]'' entry for the biggest concert ever (Paris La Defense: A City in Concert)
* 1993 – [[UNESCO Goodwill Ambassador]]&lt;ref name=&quot;Smoothoperator&quot; /&gt;
* 1994 – Victoire de la Musique for Chronologie.&lt;ref name=&quot;oxygeneconcert&quot; /&gt;
