* 1995 – Awarded [[Légion d'honneur|Chevalier de la Légion d'Honneur]] from the French Government.&lt;ref name=&quot;oxygeneconcert&quot; /&gt;
* 1997 – New ''[[Guinness Book of Records]]'' entry for the biggest concert ever with 3.5 million watching at Moscow's 850th anniversary{{cn|date=May 2020}}
* 1998 – [[IFPI]]'s [[Music recording sales certification#IFPI certification|Platinum Europe Award]]&lt;ref&gt;{{Citation | last = Masson | first = Gordon | title = Corrs to continue Jarre's IFPI role | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=PA8EAAAAMBAJ&amp;pg=PA10 | work = Billboard | date = 30 May 2000 | accessdate = 12 June 2009}}&lt;/ref&gt;{{col-2}}
