* 2006 – Polish Television Academy's &quot;Super Wiktor&quot; award for &quot;Space of Freedom&quot;
* 2006 – [[Gdańsk]]'s Man of the Year 2005 Award
* 2007 – [[Eska Awards|Eska Music Awards]] Special Award
